lead_paragraph: Technically, there are five spots available on the U.S. Olympic women's gymnastics team that will be unveiled on Sunday night at the end of Olympic Trials. But not really. And Ashton Locklear knows it.

headline.print_headline: At US Gymnastics Trials, It's a Fight for One Spot in Rio
